quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  9,111,"Mu by’ukuri, Allah yagiranye ubucuruzi n’abemera (bamuha) imitima yabo n’imitungoyabo, (abizeza) ko bazabona Ijuru. Barwana mu nzira ya Allah, bakica bakanicwa. Ni isezerano ry'ukuri yiyemeje muri Tawurati, Ivanjili na Qur’an. Ni nde wakuzuza isezerano rye kurusha Allah? Ngaho nimwishimire ubucuruzi mwagiranye na we. Uko ni ko gutsinda guhambaye"
  9,112,"(Abasezeranyijwe ijuru) ni abicuza, abagaragira (Allah), abashimira (Allah), abasiba, abunama (basenga), abubama (basenga), ababwiriza gukora ibyiza, ababuza gukora ibibi n'abarinda imbibi za Allah(bakurikiza amategeko ye). Unahe inkuru nzizaabemera (yo kuzagororerwa ijuru)"
  9,113,"Ntibikwiye ku Muhanuzi (Muhamadi)na babandi bemeye, gusabira ababangikanyamana kubabarirwa ibyaha kabone n'iyo baba bafitanye isano, nyuma y’uko bibagaragariye ko ari abo mu muriro wa Jahimu60 (kuko bapfuye ari ababangikanyamana)"
  9,114,"Nta kindi cyatumye Aburahamu asabira se kubabarirwa ibyaha, usibye ko ryari isezerano yari yaramusezeranyije. Bimaze kumugaragarira ko (se) ari umwanzi wa Allah, yitandukanyije na we. Mu by’ukuri, Aburahamu yari uwicisha bugufi cyane, Uwihanganira (ibibi akorerwa)"
  9,115,"Kandi Allah ntiyayobya abantu nyuma y’uko abayoboye,atabanje kubasobanurira ibyo birinda (batabikurikiza, bakayoba). Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Umumeyi wa byose"
  9,116,"Mu by’ukuri, Allah afite ubwami bw'ibirere n'ubw’isi. Ni we utanga ubuzima n'urupfu. Kandi nta wundi murinzi cyangwa umutabazi mwagira utari Allah"
  9,117,"Rwose Allah yamaze kwakira ukwicuza k'Umuhanuzi (Muhamadi), n’abimukira (bavuye i Maka bajya i Madina) ndetse n’abaturage b’i Madina (babakiriye), na babandi bakurikiye (Intumwa Muhamadi) mu bihe bigoye (urugamba rwa Tabuki), nyuma y’uko imitima ya bamwe muri bo yari hafi kudohoka ku kuri, maze yakira ukwicuza kwabo. Mu by'ukuri, we ni Nyiribambe, Nyirimbabazi kuri bo"
  9,118,"Kandi (Allah yakiriye ukwicuza) kwa babandi batatu61 barindirijwe (bari mu kato, bategereje ko Allah yakira ukwicuza kwabo), kugeza ubwo isi ibabanye ntoya n’ukuntu ari ngari, n'imitima yabo ikabura amahwemo; nuko bamenya ko ntaho bahungira Allah usibye kuri we. Hanyuma (Allah) yakira ukwicuza kwabo kugira ngo bamugarukire. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Uwakira ukwicuza, Nyirimbabazi"
  9,119,Yemwe abemeye! Mujye mutinya Allah kandi mube hamwe n'abanyakuri
  9,120,"Ntibikwiye ko abatuye i Madina n'Abarabu bo mu cyaro babakikije baca ukubiri n'Intumwa ya Allah, ndetse (ntibinakwiye) ko ubuzima bwabo baburutisha ubwayo. Ibyo ni ukubera ko badashobora kugira inyota, umunaniro cyangwa inzara mu nzira ya Allah, cyangwa se ngo bakandagire ahantu harakaza abahakanyi, cyangwa ngo batsinde umwanzi; ngo babure kubyandikirwa nk’ibikorwabyiza. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ntaburizamo ibihembo by'abakora ibyiza"
  9,121,"Ndetse nta n’igito cyangwa ikinini batanga (mu nzira ya Allah), cyangwa ngo bambuke ikibaya maze ngo babure kubyandikirwa, kugira ngo Allah abahembere ibyiza by'ibyo bakoraga"